  "description": "# Holograms\nAdd holograms to your PowerNukkitX Server\n\nThis plugin allows you to add floating text to your PowerNukkitX server.\nThis plugin is fully UI controllable.\n\nOpen the holograms UI with /holograms\n\nThere you can create and modify holograms.\n\n\nThis plugin supports [PlaceholderAPI](https://github.com/PowerNukkitX-Bundle/PlaceholderAPI). \nFor example, you can write %player% in a line so the players username is displayed in the hologram.\n\n<img width=\"747\" height=\"466\" alt=\"grafik\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/fa5348f8-7d79-4ade-9f32-43f552b59a0c\" />\n",
